OL,3,C'We have never seen a drug as deadly
OL,4,Cas nitazene' says senior NI coroner
OL,6,FAn inquest has found that a Dungannon
OL,7,Fman died from taking a cocktail of
OL,8,Ffive different drugs, including
OL,9,Fnitazenes.
OL,11,FMichael Maguire was found dead by his
OL,12,Fsister in December 2024.
OL,14,FOne of Northern Ireland's most senior
OL,15,Fcoroners told UTV that the synthetic
OL,16,Fopioid has a level of strength and
OL,17,Fdanger previously unseen in the region.
OL,19,FThe potent drug can be up to 500 times
OL,20,Fstronger than heroin.
