OL,3,C'We have never seen a drug as deadly
OL,4,Cas nitazene' says senior NI coroner
OL,6,FUTV was given exclusive access to a
OL,7,Ftoxicology laboratory outside Belfast,
OL,8,Fwhere biological samples are analysed
OL,9,F- including testing for drugs.
OL,11,FThere is limited information available
OL,12,Fabout nitazenes as they are relatively
OL,13,Fnew to the market.
OL,15,FTheir emergence is making the job of
OL,16,Fforensic scientists more difficult.
OL,18,FAmy Quinn said: "The analytical
OL,19,Fprocess to prepare the sample to
OL,20,Fidentify the drugs in the physical
OL,21,Fsubmissions becomes more complicated.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
