OL,3,C'We have never seen a drug as deadly
OL,4,Cas nitazene' says senior NI coroner
OL,6,F"There are a lot of rules and
OL,7,Fregulations that we have to meet in
OL,8,Fthe forensic laboratory, so the
OL,9,Fanalytical side becomes much more
OL,10,Fdifficult for new drugs," said the
OL,11,Fforensic scientist.
OL,13,F"There is interpretation associated
OL,14,Fwith drugs that have never been
OL,15,Fmedically or clinically studied.
OL,17,F"You rely on information being
OL,18,Fpublished about other detections to
OL,19,Fconsider the toxicity levels in
OL,20,Fsamples," she added.JNitazenes are
OL,21,Fbeing discovered in different forms.
