OL,3,C'We have never seen a drug as deadly
OL,4,Cas nitazene' says senior NI coroner
OL,6,F"The drug in Northern Ireland is most
OL,7,Fcommonly detected in tablets.
OL,9,F"We have seen brown powder missold as
OL,10,Fheroin which contains a nitozene," Ms
OL,11,FQuinn said.
OL,13,FThe drugs are causing local
OL,14,Fdevastation, but it is believed they
OL,15,Fare being sourced thousands of miles
OL,16,Faway in the Far East.
OL,18,FOne of Northern Ireland's most senior
OL,19,Fcoroners told UTV that the dangers of
OL,20,Fsuch drugs cannot be overstated.
