OL,3,C'We have never seen a drug as deadly
OL,4,Cas nitazene' says senior NI coroner
OL,6,FJoe McCrisken said: "The phrase
OL,7,FRussian roulette has been used by
OL,8,Fprevious coroners, but it is
OL,9,Fappropriate in this case.
OL,11,F"You may as well just roll the dice.
OL,13,F"We have never seen anything as strong
OL,14,Fas nitazene before, or as deadly.
OL,16,F"We don't know enough about the side
OL,17,Feffects of the synthetic drugs on the
OL,18,Fstreets, other than they can cause
OL,19,Fdeath," he said.
